\",\n                  \"cumulative_cost\", \"incoming_shipments\"):\n        assert field in vs\n\ndef test_get_visible_state_no_other_inventories(active_state):\n    vs = engine.get_visible_state(active_state, PlayerRole.RETAILER)\n    for role in PlayerRole:\n        if role != PlayerRole.RETAILER:\n            assert str(role) not in str(vs.get(\"players\", \"\"))\n```\n\n---\n\n### Summary table\n\n| Module | Items | Tested | Gap |\n|--------|-------|--------|-----|\n| `order_processor.py` | 4 fns | 0 | **CRITICAL** |\n| `models/order.py` | 2 classes | 0 | HIGH |\n| `models/player.py` | 2 items | 0 | HIGH |\n| `game_engine.py` edges | ~15 cases | 4 | HIGH |\n| `ai_players/rule_based.py` | 2 classes | partial | MEDIUM |\n| `reporting/` | entire module | 0 | BLOCKED (unimplemented) |\n\nBiggest bang: create `tests/core/test_order_processor.py` with the skeletons above — those 4 functions are the heart of the simulation.\n",
